	f private press records of the mid to late 70s. The band\\\, in addition t
	o Johnson\\\, features pedal steel guitarist Barry Walker\\\, keyboardist 
	Paul Hasenberg and drummer John Jeffrey who enmesh a keen sense of rhythmi
	c drive and melody with gentler\\\, sumptuous atmospheres. https://serafim
